==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Frizz
<hw>Frizz</hw>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[Partly imitative, but cf.
<er>Fry</er>.]</ety> <def>To fry, cook, or sear with a sizzling noise;
to sizzle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frizzle</ent>⟦br⟧
